<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.4">
<l>miṉṉākat teḻukiṉṟa mēkaṅkāḷ vēṅkaṭattut</l>
<l>taṉṉākat tirumaṅkai taṅkiyacīr mārvaṟku</l>
<l>eṉṉākat tiḷaṅkoṅkai virumpittām nāṭōṟum</l>
<l>poṉṉākam pulkutaṟkeṉ purivuṭaimai ceppumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O clouds from whose bodies lightning rises!</l>
<l>Do tell Him whose excellence lies in Lady Śrī dwelling on His chest in Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>That I desire to embrace [His] golden body each day,</l>
<l>with Him desiring the young breasts from my chest.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
